org.gvsig.geoprocess.algorithm.dissolve

Class DissolveRule

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.gvsig.geoprocess.algorithm.dissolve.DissolveRule
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    IDissolveRule
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    AdjacencyDissolveRule

    public class DissolveRule
extends java.lang.Object
implements IDissolveRule
    Decides if dissolve two features based in an alphanumeric criteria: two features will be dissolved if they have the same value for a given (and single) field.
